80
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,160
If the rainbow was here,

81
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:06,000
it should be a good sign to start over.

82
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,680
Look at this.

83
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,760
A rainbow.

84
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,040
Isn’t it strange?

85
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:24,600
Whenever I’m in a bad position,

86
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:28,080
