87
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:33,640
It makes me feel what I’ve experienced
wasn’t so bad.

88
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,120
You can keep it.

89
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,840
So you don’t forget

90
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,680
